  [Excerpt] The National Union for the Total Independence of 
Angola [UNITA] and the Popular Movement for the Liberation of 
Angola-Labor Party [MPLA-PT] continue to discuss peace in Lusaka 
under UN mediation. Reports from the Zambian capital yesterday 
