<F P=102>   SK3103071594 Jinan Shandong People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 2300 GMT 29 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> SK3103071594 </F>
<F P=104>  Jinan Shandong People's Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Mandarin </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] At 1200 on 29 March in Jinan's Qilu Guesthouse, Song 
Fatang, standing committee member of the provincial party 
committee and vice governor of the province, cordially met with 
Dirk Jan Van Houten, ambassador, and (Hualeiwen), commercial 
counselor of the Netherlands to China, who came to Shandong to 
inspect and visit. He welcomed the guests. 
  The purpose of the visit of Ambassador Dirk Jan Van Houten 
and his party was to promote friendly cooperative relations 
between the North Holland Province of the Netherlands and 
Shandong Province and to explore opportunities for exchange and 
cooperation in economic, cultural, and other fields. 
  Vice Governor Song Fatang introduced Shandong's reform, 
opening up, and economic development to the guests during the 
meeting. 

